thread.title: BRIEF-Diana Shipping Announces Time Charter For M/V New Orleans With SwissMarine

title: BRIEF-Diana Shipping Announces Time Charter For M/V New Orleans With SwissMarine
text: March 22, 2018 / 1:13 PM / Updated 7 minutes ago BRIEF-Diana Shipping Announces Time Charter For M/V New Orleans With SwissMarine Reuters Staff March 22 (Reuters) - Diana Shipping Inc: * DIANA SHIPPING INC. ANNOUNCES TIME CHARTER CONTRACT FOR M/V NEW ORLEANS WITH SWISSMARINE * DIANA SHIPPING INC - ‍GROSS CHARTER RATE IS US$21,000 PER DAY, MINUS A 5% COMMISSION PAID TO THIRD PARTIES​ * DIANA SHIPPING INC - ‍CHARTER IS EXPECTED TO COMMENCE ON MARCH 25, 2018​ * DIANA SHIPPING INC - EMPLOYMENT IS ANTICIPATED TO GENERATE APPROXIMATELY $6.93 MILLION OF GROSS REVENUE FOR MINIMUM SCHEDULED PERIOD OF TIME CHARTER Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
